if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為佢地叫狗公"},{"pid":"0fdd620e1e90b79fe6b45fbc1c09fe7e6dc545ec","tid":487823,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T07:17:16.000Z","msg":"因為男人無論幾濫，唔多唔少都要付出成本，點計都係蝕果個。"},{"pid":"c618e4d1966c37a61e5d2165009176bf1577a688","tid":487823,"uid":160486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T07:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解濫嘅女仔會俾人叫「臭雞」<br />\n但濫嘅男仔淨係最多俾人叫「賤男」，而完全冇出賣肉體嘅含意？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港嘅性別定型好可怕<br />\n<br />\n做男人就比人屈強姦<br />\n所以有撚就係原罪<br />\n<br />\n做女人唔係處就係原罪<br />\n濫就比人話臭雞 反而濫嘅男人最多比人話player"},{"pid":"576fbe14e04a0023eef536bd9990d28ea4372ece","tid":487823,"uid":1403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T07:20:50.000Z","msg":"因為如果一個女人肯比好多個男人出的話 生出黎只會知道邊個係老母 唔會知道邊個先係老豆<br />\n所以如果社會容許女人濫交係會造成社會問題: 咁你生左出黎 唔通要個個屌過你嘅人比一份錢臭大個仔咩? 咁個責任比邊個?"},{"pid":"124e95953d2dd8dc787342ef95d9ba1382af8996","tid":487823,"uid":19858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T07:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解濫嘅女仔會俾人叫「臭雞」<br />\n但濫嘅男仔淨係最多俾人叫「賤男」，而完全冇出賣肉體嘅含意？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<del>香港</del>連登毒撚嘅性別定型好可怕<br />\n<br />\n做男人就比人屈強姦<br />\n所以有撚就係原罪<br />\n<br />\n做女人唔係處就係原罪<br />\n濫就比人話臭雞 反而濫嘅男人最多比人話player</blockquote>"},{"pid":"cbc29